1              e             CWX.CAI_PRO1
        |
+--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------object handle              line number      object name
1              8             procedure CWX.CAI_PRO1
1              2             anonymous block

  --------------
  c: ----- PL/SQL Call Stack -----
object handle              line number      object name
